data.description: A unique opportunity! The third bedroom has not only been expanded, it also has it's own separate room that could be an office, craft room, etc. Or the entire area could be a separate living space for an extended family member. This home also features a remodeld kitchen, newer tile roof, double pane windows and sliding doors and front security doors. If you enjoy the Arizona sunshine, you will love the very private, large, tiled rear patio. There is cabinetry in the garage and rubber mats on the garage floor. Come take a look at this this home with many options.
